> Ross Morgan-Linial wrote:
> >Call me paranoid, but I am extremely suspicious of anyone who scams 
> >for a Power=4 instrument and 10 VTs, regardless of declared 
> >intentions, even if it *does* close a loophole. Also, since a Revolt 
> >is imminent anyways, I don't see it making much of a difference. 
